{"id":279236,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/维权网-西藏再次发生两位藏人自焚身亡事件（图/","date":"2013-02-15T08:01:00Z","modified":"2013-02-15T08:01:00Z","title":"维权网 | 西藏再次发生两位藏人自焚身亡事件（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员疾风报道）本网信息员刚刚获悉：西藏自治区两名藏人竹泽与叫珠巴卡，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>，分别在尼泊尔首都加德满都和甘肃勒秀乡自焚身亡。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据西藏独立作家唯色介绍，在尼泊尔首都加德满都自焚的藏人名叫竹泽，现年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>岁，甲修寺僧人。是安多果洛色达（今四川省甘孜藏族自治州色达县）洛若乡甲修村人，他的父亲是朱古桑阿丹增，母亲名叫次拉。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月，竹泽曾被拘捕</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>个月，在狱中遭受过酷刑，全身直到自焚前仍伤痕累累。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>，竹泽流亡到尼泊尔的首都加德满都，居住在西藏难民接待站，在难民接待站登记的名字是龙多丹增。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>点多，在尼泊尔首都加德满都的竹泽到博拿佛塔转经街道上，高呼“祈愿尊者达赖喇嘛永久住世”和“西藏独立”的口号，接着点火自焚，尼泊尔警察闻讯赶来灭火，将竹泽送往加德满都特里布万大学医院抢救。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>日</span><span>晚上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分，竹泽因烧伤严重，抢救无效去世。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>另一名在甘肃勒秀乡自焚的藏人名叫珠巴卡（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Drukpa Khar</span><span>），是安多黑措（今甘肃省甘南藏族自治州合作市）勒秀乡吉昂村（传统上，勒秀乡吉昂村属于阿木去乎下部部落）牧民，现年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>岁。珠巴卡的父亲名叫丹真次仁，母亲名叫丹真措。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>点多，珠巴卡在甘肃省甘南藏族自治州合作市勒秀乡自焚，当场伤重离开人世。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据知情人唯色说，珠巴卡去世后，遗下</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>岁的妻子和三个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>岁、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>岁、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>岁的孩子，一家人生活悲惨，由于当地公安的严密监控，很多珠巴卡的信息无法获知，他的照片也没有传出来。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-KYtKJ0sX-0w/UR3ob4g9sNI/AAAAAAAAdH0/m5S94aLN6vA/s1600/103-19.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-KYtKJ0sX-0w/UR3ob4g9sNI/AAAAAAAAdH0/m5S94aLN6vA/s320/103-19.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>竹泽像（网络图片）</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196,8643]}